r />\n所以唔好荒廢喺同温層外面嘅工作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:49:14.000Z","msg":"片刻不能止熄！"},{"pid":"4cf229b1a217494c4a09e656e80e1b30c30aeb94","tid":1538663,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"突破同温層！"},{"pid":"da1f9f47d497b5f19c5c5f96445a566522a186b1","tid":1538663,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:50:45.000Z","msg":"突破同温層！"},{"pid":"3e3495ead5a39d7b100e8009db67abbf664dde72","tid":1538663,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"突破同温層"},{"pid":"40b0e55c8b4065a78a0839283aea1fc67b000d13","tid":1538663,"uid":294148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"政府以為開學就會冷卻 點知唔會 之後就先出聲  由頭到尾都想孤立班後生呀"},{"pid":"1c58c3c731bae1ff20578d2713106ccf75eb2378","tid":1538663,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"推連登真心冇人睇"},{"pid":"0c4f4105c886425f02e7b6a02175c42e3ac113a4","tid":1538663,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 至今嚴重昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong>事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯\n\n袋住先 放風降溫\n大追捕 清算開始</code></pre>"},{"pid":"062c391686dcef439db7906fa8999badc91d7272","tid":1538663,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b0e55c8b4065a78a0839283aea1fc67b000d13","tid":1538663,"uid":294148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"政府以為開學就會冷卻 點知唔會 之後就先出聲  由頭到尾都想孤立班後生呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"所以要做地區工作，解釋點解唔停得"},{"pid":"b1c78581047ddc55b34ec169b67b9167533920bc","tid":1538663,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c58c3c731bae1ff20578d2713106ccf75eb2378","tid":1538663,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"推連登真心冇人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:55:00.000Z","msg":"推連登有人睇，但同温囉"},{"pid":"1ae40042d1fdd6246399fcfa27b3b82ba9f3c17c","tid":1538663,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"突破同温層"},{"pid":"c6d0fbf9cc7163db171c3fcab057c47b9efbba25","tid":1538663,"uid":294148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062c391686dcef439db7906fa8999badc91d7272","tid":1538663,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b0e55c8b4065a78a0839283aea1fc67b000d13","tid":1538663,"uid":294148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"政府以為開學就會冷卻 點知唔會 之後就先出聲  由頭到尾都想孤立班後生呀"},"citedBy":1,